name: Xtrackers MSCI World Swap UCITS ETF 1C
description_en: The Xtrackers MSCI World Swap UCITS ETF 1C seeks to track the MSCI World index. The MSCI World index tracks stocks from 23 developed countries worldwide. The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.45% p.a.. The ETF replicates the performance of the underlying index synthetically with a swap. The dividends in the ETF are accumulated and reinvested in the ETF. The Xtrackers MSCI World Swap UCITS ETF 1C is a very large ETF with 4,694m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 19 December 2006 and is domiciled in Luxembourg. Show more Show less

ETF replikuje výkon podkladového indexu synteticky s výměnou.dividenday v ETF jsou akumulovány a reinvestovány do ETF.Xtrackers MSCI World Swap UCITS ETF 1C je velmi velký ETF s spravováním 4 694 milionů euro.ETF byl spuštěn 19. prosince 2006 a má bydliště v Lucemburku.Ukázat více show méně

name: Deka DAXplus Maximum Dividend UCITS ETF
description_en: The Deka DAXplus Maximum Dividend UCITS ETF seeks to track the DAXplus® Maximum Dividend index. The DAXplus® Maximum Dividend index tracks 25 German equities with the highest dividend yield. The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.30% p.a.. The Deka DAXplus Maximum Dividend UCITS ETF is the only ETF that tracks the DAXplus® Maximum Dividend index. The ETF replicates the performance of the underlying index by full replication (buying all the index constituents). The dividends in the ETF are distributed to the investors (Quarterly). The Deka DAXplus Maximum Dividend UCITS ETF has 253m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 3 April 2009 and is domiciled in Germany. Show more Show less

name: Vanguard S&P 500 UCITS ETF (USD) Distributing
description_en: The Vanguard S&P 500 UCITS ETF (USD) Distributing seeks to track the S&P 500® index. The S&P 500® index tracks the 500 largest US stocks. The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.07% p.a.. The ETF replicates the performance of the underlying index by full replication (buying all the index constituents). The dividends in the ETF are distributed to the investors (Quarterly). The Vanguard S&P 500 UCITS ETF (USD) Distributing is a very large ETF with 41,765m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 22 May 2012 and is domiciled in Ireland. Show more Show less

name: SPDR MSCI World UCITS ETF
description_en: The SPDR MSCI World UCITS ETF seeks to track the MSCI World index. The MSCI World index tracks stocks from 23 developed countries worldwide. The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.12% p.a.. The ETF replicates the performance of the underlying index by sampling technique (buying a selection of the most relevant index constituents). The dividends in the ETF are accumulated and reinvested in the ETF. The SPDR MSCI World UCITS ETF is a very large ETF with 12,307m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 28 February 2019 and is domiciled in Ireland. Show more Show less
